content: Hi Rowan, I saw Gamma Labs is in Houston. Which big ideas keep getting pushed because no one has time?
What do I tell you that?
I am just curious what is on your to-do list that never gets done. what is one thing you wish ran smoother?
Just like while you're asking me these type of questions, I don't want to tell anyone about my business.
I understand completely, Rowan. what is one small daily hassle you'd love to fix?
Well, not from you guys. I should accept you.
No problem at all, Rowan. Could I ask who you usually work with for your tech or marketing needs?
Well, we have a free housing marketing team and we don't need tech support as much as we think.
Well I don't need any marketing support or tech support from you guys.
